data.description: This charming four bedroom, two bath ranch provides an exceptional amount of space! The original footprint of the home offers a spacious living room, an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, three bedrooms, and a full bath with ceramic tile shower and floor. The kitchen opens up to the addition that was constructed in 1998. The addition includes a large dining room, spacious owner's suite with a walk-in closet, and an owner's bath containing a ceramic tile shower and floors. The attached two-car garage has ample space for additional storage. Laminate floors in kitchen, dining room, and all bedrooms make for easy living. The fenced-in back yard and deck are a great place to enjoy the upcoming spring weather! The grill is connected to a dedicated gas line and remains with the home. A home security system featuring one interior camera and several exterior cameras is also included. Recent updates include new HVAC and water heater about four years ago, new roof about five years ago, and gutter helmet installed last year. Seller offering a one-year home warranty. Come see all this home has to offer!
